Vasuki Account Deletion Request

If you want to delete your Vasuki account and associated data, you can request deletion by email.

How to request account deletion
Send an email to udayanverma@gmail.com from the same email address you used in the Vasuki app.
Use subject line: Delete my Vasuki account.
In the email body, include:
Your registered app email
Your full name (optional)
Confirmation: “I request deletion of my Vasuki account and associated data.”
What will be deleted
When your request is processed, we will delete:

Your account profile data
Authentication-linked account data
User-generated data associated with your account (where applicable)
What may be retained
We may retain limited records only where required for:

Legal, security, fraud-prevention, or compliance purposes
Deletion timeline
Standard processing time: within 30 days of verified request.
If additional verification is required, processing may take longer.
Contact
For deletion and privacy requests, contact: udayanverma@gmail.com

